Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:09.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Soon another piece of cutting-edge European technology will be delivered to the International Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:09.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,很快 另一项欧洲的尖端技术将被送到国际空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:13.51,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,ERA, short for European Robotic Arm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:13.51,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA是欧洲机械臂的简称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:17.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,will be launched on a proton rocket from the Baikonur cosmodrome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:17.10,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,将由一枚质子火箭从拜科努尔航天发射场发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:21.07,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,together with the Russian Multipurpose Laboratory Module, Nauka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:21.07,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,与俄罗斯多用途实验舱 "Nauka "一起发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:27.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This brand-new Russian module will be ERA's home base for the next ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:27.08,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这个全新的俄罗斯模块将成为ERA未来10年的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:32.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The 11-metre long ERA-arm can lift up to 8 tons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:32.04,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,11米长的ERA-臂可以举起8吨重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:36.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and be operated with an accuracy of an astonishing 5 millimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:36.92,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,并能以惊人的5毫米的精度进行操作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,One of the most impressive features of the robotic arm is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,该机械臂最令人印象深刻的特点之一是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.84,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,that it can move hand-over-hand over the Russian module.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.84,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它可以在俄罗斯舱内手拉手地移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The ERA-arm is almost completely symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.88,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA-臂几乎是完全对称的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This means it has a hand or an end-effector at both sides
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.62,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这意味着它在两边都有一只手或一个末端执行器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.57,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and that each side can serve as the tip as well as the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.57,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而且每一侧都可以作为尖端和肩部的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So it means that if you have multiple base points on the on the Russian segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.54,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因此 这意味着 如果你在俄罗斯段上有多个基点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,you can go from one base point to the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.31,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以从一个基点到另一个基点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:07.01,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,then release your shoulder, which becomes tip,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:07.01,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,然后释放你的肩膀 成为尖端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and then manipulate a payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.68,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,然后操纵一个有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So in that sense, it has freedom of motion on the Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.48,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以在这个意义上 它在空间站上有运动自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:16.32,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,With this freedom of motion and well-chosen location
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:16.32,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,有了这种运动自由和精心选择的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.32,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,ERA will be able to service the Russian segment of the Space Station
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.32,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA将能够为空间站的俄罗斯部分提供服务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.41,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,which is not in reach of the other two robotic arms already installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.41,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是已安装的另外两个机器人手臂所不能达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:29.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,ERA is fully programmable and has several modes of automation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:29.85,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA是完全可编程的 有几种自动化模式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This means each mission can be prepared on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.98,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这意味着每个任务都可以在地面上进行准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and then uploaded into the arm's computer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.62,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,然后上传到机械臂的计算机中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:41.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,after which the astronauts onboard can run and authorize each step of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:41.96,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,之后 船上的宇航员可以运行并授权任务的每一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:48.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Theoretically ERA could even work autonomously and run the mission all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:48.28,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,理论上 ERA甚至可以自主工作 完全自己运行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.29,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It also offers the possibility for astronauts on board
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.29,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它还为船上的宇航员提供了可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,to piece together a new mission on the fly if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.26,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果有必要的话 它还可以在飞行中拼凑出一个新的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:59.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The arm will have several important applications
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:59.23,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,该机械臂将有几个重要的应用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:03.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,to alleviate the work of the astronauts on the International Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:03.02,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,减轻国际空间站上宇航员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.22,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,As crew time is precious and the safety of astronauts is paramount
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.22,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,由于船员的时间是宝贵的 而且宇航员的安全是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,the arm can be used for tasks which are described as the three D's,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.34,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,该机械臂可用于被描述为三个D的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Dull, Dangerous and Difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.85,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,沉闷、危险和困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The robotic arm can be used for, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.10,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,该机械臂可用于 例如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:25.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,take payloads out of an airlock autonomously without the risk of an extra vehicular activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:25.27,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,自主地将有效载荷从气闸中取出 而不需要额外的车辆活动的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.47,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,for example, and put equipment on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.47,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,例如 将设备放在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It can be used for inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.34,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它可以用于检查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:36.17,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It can be used for putting big new modules, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:36.17,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它可以用来放置大的新模块 例如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and putting it on the Space Station, move big things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.38,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,并把它放在空间站上 移动大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:46.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And also it can be used to help the cosmonauts when they are doing a spacewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:46.26,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当宇航员进行太空行走时 它也可以被用来帮助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,to move cosmonauts around or big payloads
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.02,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,来移动宇航员或大的有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:53.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,while the astronauts and cosmonauts have their hands free to work on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:53.66,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而宇航员和宇航员可以腾出手来在外面工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.37,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So it can be used in several ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.37,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因此 它可以在几个方面使用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:59.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,ERA has been specially designed for collaboration between man and machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:59.96,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA是专门为人与机器之间的协作而设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:05.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The astronauts can even operate the arm from outside the Space Station during spacewalks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:05.56,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,宇航员甚至可以在太空行走期间从空间站外操作机械臂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:11.67,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,using a remote control which has been optimized to be used by astronauts in bulky space suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:11.67,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,使用一个经过优化的遥控器 供穿着笨重太空服的宇航员使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.01,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,French ESA astronaut Thomas Pesquet who is currently at the Space Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.01,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,目前在空间站的法国欧空局宇航员Thomas Pesquet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:21.75,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,will be involved in ERA's commissioning when the arm first arrives at the Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:21.75,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,将在ERA机械臂首次到达空间站时参与其调试工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Later, Mathias Maurer and Samantha Cristoforetti
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,随后 马蒂亚斯-毛雷尔和萨曼莎-克里斯托弗雷蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:31.21,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,will take part in the installation and operation of ERA through various spacewalks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:31.21,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,将通过各种太空行走参与ERA的安装和操作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.79,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,One of ERA's first tasks will be to install the radiator and airlock of the NAUKA module
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.79,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA的首要任务之一将是安装NAUKA模块的散热器和气闸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.64,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,so the laboratory can become operational
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.64,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,以便该实验室能够开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:47.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and ERA can use this airlock to move payloads from inside the Station to outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:47.18,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA可以利用这个气闸将有效载荷从空间站内转移到站外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.32,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,When we operate the ERA on the ISS,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.32,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当我们在国际空间站上操作ERA的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.45,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,as we're obviously going to learn a lot about how to use robots in space
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.45,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因为我们显然会学到很多关于如何在太空中使用机器人的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and how the robots work in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.68,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,以及机器人如何在太空中工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:02.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,We'll have feedback to our engineering process
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:02.09,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我们将有反馈给我们的工程进程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:07.19,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,if we finally know, what is the performance during its use in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:07.19,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果我们最终知道 在太空中使用时的性能是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,We also learn on what we can best do with robots
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.48,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我们还学习了我们可以用机器人做的最好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and what we can best do with people and learn about the cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.87,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,和我们能最好地与人一起做什么 并学习合作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:20.05,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And all of that is going to be very, very useful when we would go further into the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:20.05,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所有这些将是非常非常有用的 当我们将进一步进入宇宙时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:25.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and still have for sure robots initially, but maybe at some point in time also people with robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:25.09,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而且最初肯定还是有机器人 但也许在某个时间点也会有人和机器人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:30.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,We're really looking forward to all what we can learn from the experience on the ISS with ERA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:30.40,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我们真的很期待我们能从国际空间站上的ERA的经验中学到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,ERA is another example of cooperation between Europe and Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.85,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,ERA是欧洲和俄罗斯之间合作的另一个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and a tribute to the excellence of European industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.85,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,是欧洲和俄罗斯之间合作的另一个例子 也是对欧洲工业的卓越成就的一种赞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:43.13,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The project was commissioned by ESA and largely funded by the Dutch government
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:43.13,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,该项目由欧空局委托 主要由荷兰政府资助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:47.05,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,with Airbus Defence and Space Netherlands as its prime contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:47.05,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,空中客车防务和空间公司荷兰分公司是其主要承包商
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Now the European Robotic Arm will fly to the ISS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.52,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,现在 欧洲机器人手臂将飞往国际空间站
